De Vere Says CEO Balfour-Lynn, CFO Singh to Leave Company

-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 
2011-09-19T06:11:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/de-vere-says-ceo-balfour-lynn-cfo-singh-to-leave-company.html
De Vere Group Ltd. said Chief
Executive Officer Richard Balfour-Lynn and Chief Financial
Officer Jag Singh have decided to step down from the board and
are leaving the company to focus on other business interests.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Altaner in London at 
 daltaner@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
